des: The daily health update with Dr. Dom covers a wide range of diet, exercise, and health topics. Some updates will be very short and motivational while others longer and educations. This information should not be substituted for medical or chiropractic advice. Any and all health care concerns, decisions, and actions must be done through the advice and counsel of a health care professional who is familiar with your updated medical history. For more information about Dr. Taylor please visit www.osochiro.com
